  "texts": [
    "This also causes ambiguity for the NER system.",
    "Another challenge in Urdu NER is the typographic errors of certain characters that are often made by the writers due to character similarity or character variance leading to confusion in orthographical representations.",
    "Due to inconsistencies in writing styles, the same NEs may be assigned an incorrect entity type [44].",
    "For instance, the word Saif, written as \" вАЂпЇївАђ вАЂпѓњвАђ вАЂпїТвАђ \" and \" вАЂпЇ≥вАђ вАЂпѓњвАђ вАЂпїТвАђ \", may get different NE labels due to the writing variations.",
    "This section discusses the existing studies on NER for the Urdu language that mainly use three approaches; (i) rule-based, (ii) ML and DL-based, and (iii) hybrid approach."
